      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<div class=\"contentLayout2\">\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p>PxrAovLight is a handy utility light that allows a lighting artist to output a shot-specific AOV mask without needing to request one from the shading artists.</p><h3 id=\"PxrAovLightinKatana-LightLinkingwithPxrAovLight\">Light Linking with PxrAovLight</h3><p>Use light linking to include/exclude pieces of geometry in the AOV. In this example, the PxrAovLight is &quot;off&quot; globally and &quot;on&quot; the tree in the scene.  This linking set up creates creates a mask of the tree.</p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-equal\" data-layout=\"two-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"632\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/546178440/rfkPxrAovLight_primary.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531532170&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=512&amp;height=512\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/546178440/rfkPxrAovLight_primary.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531532170&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"512\" data-width=\"512\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"546178461\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfkPxrAovLight_primary.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"546178440\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"6b8f60b3-f8fa-4449-af3f-9fde0cc2874d\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/546178440/rfkPxrAovLight_primary.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531532170&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=512&amp;height=512 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/546178440/rfkPxrAovLight_primary.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531532170&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=512&amp;height=512 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"632\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/546178440/rfkPxrAovLight_mask.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531532170&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=512&amp;height=512\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/546178440/rfkPxrAovLight_mask.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531532170&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"512\" data-width=\"512\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"546178464\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfkPxrAovLight_mask.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"546178440\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"6037d572-2cc6-46b2-98b1-4d638980ec32\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/546178440/rfkPxrAovLight_mask.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531532170&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=512&amp;height=512 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/546178440/rfkPxrAovLight_mask.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531532170&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=512&amp;height=512 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"632\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/546178440/rfkPxrAovLight_linking.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531531961&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=632&amp;height=585\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/546178440/rfkPxrAovLight_linking.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531531961&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"630\" data-width=\"680\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"546178455\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfkPxrAovLight_linking.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"546178440\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"5725128d-8d1e-40bf-9ef0-5064950a7076\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/546178440/rfkPxrAovLight_linking.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531531961&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=680&amp;height=630 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/546178440/rfkPxrAovLight_linking.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531531961&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=632&amp;height=585 1x\"></span><h3 id=\"PxrAovLightinKatana-LightFiltersandPxrAovLight\">Light Filters and PxrAovLight</h3><p>Because PxrAovLight is a &quot;light&quot;, light linking and light filters can modify the output AOV.  In this example, the PxrIntMultLightFilter is attached to PxrAovLight.  The Light Filter is only linked to the tree trunk, resulting in a gray value for the tree trunk mask.</p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-equal\" data-layout=\"two-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"632\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/546178440/rfkPxrAovLight_primary.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531532170&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=512&amp;height=512\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/546178440/rfkPxrAovLight_primary.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531532170&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"512\" data-width=\"512\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"546178461\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfkPxrAovLight_primary.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"546178440\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"6b8f60b3-f8fa-4449-af3f-9fde0cc2874d\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/546178440/rfkPxrAovLight_primary.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531532170&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=512&amp;height=512 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/546178440/rfkPxrAovLight_primary.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531532170&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=512&amp;height=512 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" width=\"632\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/546178440/rfkPxrAovLight_filteredMask.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531532170&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=512&amp;height=512\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/546178440/rfkPxrAovLight_filteredMask.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531532170&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"512\" data-width=\"512\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"546178467\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfkPxrAovLight_filteredMask.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"546178440\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"06a14ce3-93cf-46d5-970f-18a7d3254991\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/546178440/rfkPxrAovLight_filteredMask.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531532170&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=512&amp;height=512 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/546178440/rfkPxrAovLight_filteredMask.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531532170&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=512&amp;height=512 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/546178440/rfkPxrAovLight_lightFilter.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531531961&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/546178440/rfkPxrAovLight_lightFilter.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531531961&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"610\" data-width=\"665\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"546178458\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfkPxrAovLight_lightFilter.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"546178440\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"5b083ab4-7199-4550-9fcd-dca015995f27\" data-media-type=\"file\"></span><h3 id=\"PxrAovLightinKatana-DefiningtheOutputAOV\">Defining the Output AOV</h3><p>Use the PrmanOutputChannelDefine and RenderOutputDefine nodes to create the AOV to which PxrAovLight will write.  These three parameters should all be the same<strong>:</strong></p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table data-table-width=\"1800\" data-layout=\"default\" data-local-id=\"30c2db55-592e-412c-98a0-660b11a9fbcd\" class=\"confluenceTable\"><tbody><tr><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p><strong>PxrAovLight</strong></p></td><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p><em>AOV Name</em></p></td></tr><tr><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p><strong>PrmanChannelOutputDefine</strong></p></td><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p><em>name</em></p></td></tr><tr><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p><strong>RenderOutputDefine</strong></p></td><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p><em>channel</em></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"960\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/546178440/rfkPxrAovLight_channelName.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531531961&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=960&amp;height=372\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/546178440/rfkPxrAovLight_channelName.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531531961&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"497\" data-width=\"1280\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"546178452\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfkPxrAovLight_channelName.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"546178440\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"86f1a707-38b7-424d-a59c-ced88f07b848\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/546178440/rfkPxrAovLight_channelName.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531531961&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1575&amp;height=611 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/546178440/rfkPxrAovLight_channelName.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531531961&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=960&amp;height=372 1x\"></span><p><span class=\"legacy-color-text-red2\"> </span></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
    }
